## Java Recursion Basics

This repository contains simple Java recursion programs commonly asked in
automation testing and Java interviews.

### Programs Included
- Print numbers using recursion (forward & backward)
- Factorial of a number
- Fibonacci series
- Sum of digits
- Reverse a string
- Count digits in a number

### Key Concepts Covered
- Base condition
- Recursive call
- Call stack
- Backtracking
